<br />
<br />change_white:
<br />
<br />lda trig  ;  trig is set in the code which detects the pulling of trigger
<br />cmp #17
<br />bne sex
<br />
<br />lda white_var
<br />cmp #0
<br />bne check1
<br />
<br />lda #1
<br />sta $512
<br />sta $50e
<br />sta $50a
<br />lda #0
<br />sta $506
<br />inc white_var
<br />
<br />jsr poll
<br />lda whitevar
<br />cmp #1
<br />bne doo1 
<br />INC $507 ; simply just to see if it works
